column5: It looks as if I am going to Vancouver 2010!  Mens Hockey Canada vs USA x 4 tickets Womens Freestyle Skiing x 4 Closing ceremony x 3  My brother wont leave me alone now haha  Wondering if anyone else got tickets through the lottery draw? I'm going to try again in 09 to get some more.
Hey buddy, long time - no see... we should hookup again sometime  Good job scoring some tickets. Women's freestyle? Is that skiing or skating? -Brian
Freestyle Skiing. iv always enjoyed watching it. I am pumped!
I bet! Don't forget your cowbells!
congrats on the score, hope u have a blast  just curious how the lottery works, never heard of it  ps. better book ur hotel soon,
